abstract: At least 38 women and girls traveling by truck to a traditional festival in Swaziland are killed when truck collides with another vehicle.
lead_paragraph: Dozens of women and girls were traveling to a traditional festival, but an advocacy group said that details of the accident were hard to come by.

headline.main: 38 People Killed in Truck Crash in Swaziland
headline.print_headline: Deadly Crash Before Festival in Swaziland
